in\": 684, \"end\": 689, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996948645, \"rank\": 3.0505479843535517e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For more of our coverage from the Games, head toour latest updates.\", \"from\": 720, \"to\": 787, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Lucia Moris of South Sudan toppled to the ground in agony during a preliminary heat of the women's 100-meter race at the Paris Olympics on Friday.\", \"from\": 789, \"to\": 935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 789, \"end\": 794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Devil_May_Cry\", \"score\": 0.9997560380276204, \"rank\": 0.00024397616186654686, \"text\": \"Lucia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Devil_May_Cry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Devil_May_Cry\"}, {\"begin\": 795, \"end\": 800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But before medics arrived, someone else rushed to her side: fellow competitor Silina Pha Aphay of Laos.\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1040, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1015, \"end\": 1021, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silina\", \"score\": 0.9999999366450558, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Silina\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silina\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Silina\"}, {\"begin\": 1035, \"end\": 1039, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"score\": 0.9999973676743223, \"rank\": 2.3915185430497237e-06, \"text\": \"Laos\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Moris, in Lane 1, was keeping pace after bolting from the starting blocks.\", \"from\": 1042, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But halfway through the race, she began to slow down and look unsteady, before crumpling to the ground.\", \"from\": 1117, \"to\": 1220, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The fall occurred in front of Pha Aphay, who was in Lane 2.\", \"from\": 1221, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1251, \"end\": 1254, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"score\": 0.9467599957951466, \"rank\": 0.056151140479579434, \"text\": \"Pha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The South Sudanese athlete laid on the purple track, unable to get back up.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1286, \"end\": 1300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\", \"score\": 0.9999646514685958, \"rank\": 3.534978104294971e-05, \"text\": \"South Sudanese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Sudan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Even after the race ended, Moris, 23, remained on the ground alone, shrieking in pain and clutching her right thigh.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1474, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1390, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lucia Moris, of South Sudan, fell halfway through a preliminary heat for the women's 100-meter run at the Paris Olympics on Friday.Petr David Josek/APhide caption  That's when Pha Aphay, 28, ran back toward Moris.\", \"from\": 1476, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1476, \"end\": 1481, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Devil_May_Cry\", \"score\": 0.9997560380276204, \"rank\": 0.00024397616186654686, \"text\": \"Lucia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Devil_May_Cry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Characters_of_Devil_May_Cry\"}, {\"begin\": 1482, \"end\": 1487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}, {\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"score\": 0.9467599957951466, \"rank\": 0.056151140479579434, \"text\": \"Pha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\"}, {\"begin\": 1683, \"end\": 1688, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Laotian had just finished sixth, which was not high enough to advance to the next stage.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1782, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1694, \"end\": 1701, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"score\": 0.9999680121996178, \"rank\": 2.9561360461853664e-05, \"text\": \"Laotian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laos\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And so, her time at the Olympics was over.\", \"from\": 1783, \"to\": 1825, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But in that moment, Pha Aphay's first action was to go to the distressed Moris.\", \"from\": 1827, \"to\": 1906, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1847, \"end\": 1850, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"score\": 0.9467599957951466, \"rank\": 0.056151140479579434, \"text\": \"Pha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\"}, {\"begin\": 1900, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Standing beside Moris, Pha Aphay called out for help.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1924, \"end\": 1929, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}, {\"begin\": 1931, \"end\": 1934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"score\": 0.9467599957951466, \"rank\": 0.056151140479579434, \"text\": \"Pha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once medics arrived, Pha Aphay continued to stay on the track, holding Moris' sneakers while medics prepared to put Moris on a stretcher.\", \"from\": 1962, \"to\": 2099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1983, \"end\": 1986, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"score\": 0.9467599957951466, \"rank\": 0.056151140479579434, \"text\": \"Pha\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Potentially_hazardous_object\"}, {\"begin\": 2033, \"end\": 2038, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}, {\"begin\": 2078, \"end\": 2083, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another competitor, Salam Bouha Ahamdy of Mauritania, later also appeared to support Moris.\", \"from\": 2100, \"to\": 2191, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2120, \"end\": 2125, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdus_Salam\", \"score\": 0.9889823363929361, \"rank\": 0.011139670659805782, \"text\": \"Salam\", \"types\": [\"Q901\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdus_Salam\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abdus_Salam\"}, {\"begin\": 2185, \"end\": 2190, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"score\": 0.9998710749806742, \"rank\": 0.0001289416431762218, \"text\": \"Moris\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mauritius\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"All 100 meters athletes have to know how being hurt feels.\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2252, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And this is a big competition.\", \"from\": 2253, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's a big dream to come here.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2314, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But you get hurt here.\", \"from\": 2315, \"to\": 2337, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"So everybody knows the feeling,\\\